Concept
=======
Detection of <.
Detection of type of tag.
-> special detection.

First version:
- Main tags. 
  - <tag>
  - <!-- comment -->
  - <?instruction?>
  - <![%foo[<!ELEMENT foo EMPTY>]]>
  - <![CDATA[<text>text</text>]]>
  - <!DOCTYPE [ <!ELEMENT foo EMPTY> ]>

Seond version:
- Main tags.
- Parse long tags to subtags.
